gov.usgs.anss.edge

Class EdgeBlockPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.edge.EdgeBlockPool

  • public final class EdgeBlockPool
extends java.lang.Object
    This class forms a pool of EdgeBlocks which can be allocated and freed, but not run through the garbage collector. Used mainly by EdgeBlockClient for making the IndexFile collection which must be freed when completed.
